Russia Offers to Help Europe on Debt if Clear Program Presented

-- B y   A l e n a   C h e c h e l
-- 
2011-10-10T07:52:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/russia-offers-to-help-europe-on-debt-if-clear-program-presented.html
Russia’s government is ready to help
European countries overcome the continent’s sovereign debt
crisis if officials present a clear bailout program, said  Arkady
Dvorkovich , President  Dmitry Medvedev ’s chief economic adviser,
in Moscow today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
